OL,3,C'A laughing stock': Irish signs judge
OL,4,Cblasts Executive use of court to solve
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe Stormont Executive should attempt
OL,8,Fto resolve a row over Irish language
OL,9,Fsigns at Belfast's Grand Central
OL,10,FStation and avoid being seen as a
OL,11,F"laughing stock", a High Court judge
OL,12,Furged today.
OL,14,FMr Justice McAlinden called on
OL,15,Fministers to enter discussions instead
OL,16,Fof spending vital public money being
OL,17,Fon opposing sides in a legal battle.
