OL,4,Cblasts Executive use of court to solve
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FPutting back a challenge mounted by
OL,8,Floyalist activist Jamie Bryson, he
OL,9,Fdeclared it a test for the power-
OL,10,Fsharing administration to demonstrate
OL,11,Fpolitical consensus can be reached on
OL,12,Fissues of dispute.
OL,14,FFunding for the case could instead go
OL,15,Ftowards tackling the "parlous" state
OL,16,Fof Northern Ireland's health service
OL,17,Fand infrastructure, or pollution in
OL,18,FLough Neagh, it was suggested.
