OL,4,Cblasts Executive use of court to solve
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"We need as a society to have a grown-
OL,8,Fup Executive that works together, not
OL,9,Fadopting a silo mentality and throwing
OL,10,Fbrush shafts into each other's spokes
OL,11,Ffor political gain," the judge
OL,12,Finsisted.
OL,14,F"It's not working...we are being
OL,15,Fregarded as a laughing stock.
OL,17,F"We have moved on from killing each
OL,18,Fother, but we haven't moved much
OL,19,Ffurther from that.
