OL,7,FCiting their reported combined
OL,8,Fsalaries of up to #180,000, Mr Justice
OL,9,FMcAlinden indicated the commissioners
OL,10,Fshould also be consulted in a bid to
OL,11,Fdefuse the argument.
OL,13,F"If there is still disagreement we can
OL,14,Fcome back to court and address Mr
OL,15,FByrson's challenge," the judge said.
OL,17,FAt one point Tony McGleenan KC,
OL,18,Frepresenting the Department for
OL,19,FInfrastructure, claimed two ministers
OL,20,Fbeing in court on opposing sides was
OL,21,Fan indication of political failure.
