OL,7,FMr Justice McAlinden responded by
OL,8,Fhighlighting the potentially cost-
OL,9,Feffective alternatives resolutions,
OL,10,Fand the separate roles performed by
OL,11,Fthe judiciary and legislature.
OL,13,F"Running to court every time something
OL,14,Flike this happens - if the Executive
OL,15,Fwas functioning properly I'm not sure
OL,16,Fthere would be the need for people
OL,17,Flike Mr Bryson to raise these issues,"
OL,18,Fhe observed.
